{"TopicId":144563,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Gertry\u0026#039;s General Gyrocopters","CreatedByName":"MatttheCzar","CreatedById":135304,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-25T23:53:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"MatttheCzar","CreatedById":135304,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-25T23:53:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGGG is the first and last word in gyrocopters. \u00A0Or autogyros. \u00A0Gyroplanes? \u00A0Whatever you like to call them, GGG has them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThe G-1 Gladiator:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis gyrocopter was the very first made for the military. \u00A0While air force officials were at first skeptical of the craft as it sat on the runway, their expectations were blown away;\u00A0not only was the gyro\u00A0capable of taking off like an STOL, it also was able to turn\u00A0on a dime, then quickly recover to its top speed of \u0026gt;200 m/s. \u00A0It now is commonly used in areas where full runways are not able to be built, as well as right behind the front line, where it makes a great ground attack vehicle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022rtc7GJk.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/rtc7GJk.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLook, Ma! \u00A0No rotor thrust!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Cbzt6d3.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Cbzt6d3.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeres how that works:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022aVM2w9n.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/aVM2w9n.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDue to the real life phenomenon of autorotation, the rotor works like a wing!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022HuTck21.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/HuTck21.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00225VW803n.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/5VW803n.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022JhPWrq8.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/JhPWrq8.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022eROlsfN.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/eROlsfN.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022imgur-embed-pub\u0022 lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EFlying instructions:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Turn on jet engine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Move forwards until you\u00A0are going at around 50 m/s\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. Take off... that\u0027s it! \u00A0You can turn on the rotor a little at the beginning so its spinning more at takeoff, but otherwise it flies\u00A0like a plane.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDownload:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/home?preview=G-1.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/home?preview=G-1.craft\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s also the G-1E, a version with an ejector for the rotor in emergencies:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/home?preview=G-1E.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/home?preview=G-1E.craft\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRequires KAX and Tweakscale.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThe G-2 Mini:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAn ultralight gyro one of my test pilots, Jeb, designed and built during\u00A0his spare time at work. \u00A0Shows great initiative, that kerbal, maybe he\u0027ll be a spacekerman someday.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022w7Zad0c.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/w7Zad0c.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShowoff!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022qtnlZV0.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/qtnlZV0.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022TrZZceE.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/TrZZceE.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022sH9vMrN.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/sH9vMrN.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDownload:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/home?preview=G-2\u002BMini.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/home?preview=G-2\u002BMini.craft\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRequires KAX and Tweakscale.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-26T01:43:05Z\u0022 title=\u002207/26/2016 01:43  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 26, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by MatttheCzar\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rune","CreatedById":52690,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-26T00:17:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAutorotation is a \u003Cem\u003Every\u003C/em\u003E cool aerodynamic concept. And even tough it\u0027s practiced by \u003Cem\u003Eall\u003C/em\u003E helicopter pilots, it\u0027s a concept rarely known outside the field. Glad to see autogyros in KSP!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRune. Also, it was a Spanish guy that came up with the idea. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MatttheCzar","CreatedById":135304,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-26T00:38:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222691024\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022144563\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221469492276\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002252690\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rune\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, Rune said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAutorotation is a \u003Cem\u003Every\u003C/em\u003E cool aerodynamic concept. And even tough it\u0027s practiced by \u003Cem\u003Eall\u003C/em\u003E helicopter pilots, it\u0027s a concept rarely known outside the field. Glad to see autogyros in KSP!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRune. Also, it was a Spanish guy that came up with the idea. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks! \u00A0I think I\u0027ll try to make the original gyrocopter soon.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/4f/Ciervas_1st_autogiro.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022Ciervas_1st_autogiro.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MatttheCzar","CreatedById":135304,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-26T01:43:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew gyro ready for download!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022qtnlZV0.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/qtnlZV0.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}